Title: The Endless Swarm
Description: Gao-ran's men need help down on the southern front. If you want to stand by the Shado-Pan, that's where you should do it.
ObjectivesText: Kill 12 Krik'thik attackers at the Gao-Ran Battlefront.
RewardText: The men of the battlefront are growing to respect you. You clearly know how to fight.
